{"tid":1464600,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我係地勤關於機場我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:03:57.000Z","uid":118592,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a3323f3979233f26248dcf773a8880072bc0a136","tid":1464600,"uid":118592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:14:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係分化撚，想分化吓大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分你老母呀！講好左不割蓆、不篤灰、不分化架嘛。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我借朋友 ac 出 post，有啲野我係一定要講。<br />\n<br />\n我其實都有落場周圍行下睇下、對於今日發生既事我有少少睇法。<br />\n<br />\n首先我都好明大家琴日因為解散軍既fake news而搞到散水好唔gur，今日好想再塞多次機場同時向外國旅客表達返大家既訴求。<br />\n<br />\n但係今日塞機場既，我可以話比大家知，你一D成就都冇拎過。<br />\n<br />\nAA今日根本冇取消機，只係唔開check in，而家入面只做轉機客，咁你冇cancel到班機但又唔比客check in，最後落左邊個數？唔係777、唔係AA，而家落左大家數。天琦擔心我哋，特登响獄中寫信俾我哋，「我們必須反思自己的每一言一行，會使我們離這個目標更近還是更遠！」如果你响機場已經冇效果，就散啦！<br />\n<br />\n已經有好多外國鬼佬鬼婆唔係屌AA，而係屌緊大家唔比佢出發，再係咁落去大家係出面點浪費口水都冇用，甚至比到位777做你。 同第一次和你飛完美地一紙不留相比，係印象分嘅問題啊。 屌港人，阻港人返工， 你仲可以話佢廢老，話佢港豬。你而家屌啲遊客，做乜9？你唔係要國際支持咩？仲話眾籌去外國登報搵要國際關注，不如留返啲錢買飛機杯仲好！<br />\n<br />\n仲有噴漆啊，係核爆都唔割，但係要搞啱對象！個機場冇得罪你，唔好搞，Aa已經好合作。世界上冇幾多個機場會有graffiti架！你玩壞左機場，要遊學嘅話點算！<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記航空公司好多地勤同事都用緊自己方法支持你哋，尋日啲機取消晒都幫你哋頂，三罷亦令二百幾班機取消， 唔好再俾位人哋入啦！<br />\n<br />\n你地睇下，一單小事就搞到你地分化、互屌，中晒劉業成計呀！一人打自己一巴。打醒自己，再一齊爬山！屌完唔好再嬲唔好再嘈，記住五大訴求，同818大遊行呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F3Mz8ei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF3Mz8ei.jpg&h=464388a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f541a155b1116e228d27e8e9f50a729309e5591d","tid":1464600,"uid":75702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"390fd45ecfce543d23c89428f28b66448a44595c","tid":1464600,"uid":17381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"122b380ae4ec8b3bc335878c30ced856343ab757","tid":1464600,"uid":102719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:18:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n依家機場好危險"},{"pid":"c47bf6fc8973bba206c57b1cc6dae86844cd6a00","tid":1464600,"uid":42665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:19:15.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bda0d1151c710958c26ae02ccc86b4db9d420b4","tid":1464600,"uid":42665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:19:40.000Z","msg":"721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870255bcab936a1dd4d4b37753f0728ed450baf7","tid":1464600,"uid":196861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:20:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ccf28f06ef4d13602c29865fb2b6f75f9e026644","tid":1464600,"uid":273307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:22:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f819fef91f34adde8d0d756fd0c09eb0ff7dffb0","tid":1464600,"uid":35686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:22:47.000Z","msg":"well well"},{"pid":"536a5b5d890d6578af7222a9c486bf24ce1091b0","tid":1464600,"uid":118592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa